### EXISTING STRUCTURES
None

### ERROR TIPS
-  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items
- Ensure you can place a entity to a tile before attempting placing
### Errors when placing an entity but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target position where you want to place the entity before placing it. The maximum distance to place an entity is 10.

### NAMESPACE
None
